## 4. Backend API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/signal/current` | GET | Returns current signal or "no signal" state for given instrument |
| `/signal/history` | GET | Returns all past signals with outcomes |
| `/range/today` | GET | Returns today's London High and London Low |
| `/price/live` | GET | Returns current price for XAUUSD or BTCUSD |
| `/explain` | POST | Sends signal data to Snwolley Agents API, returns plain English explanation |
| `/voice` | POST | Sends explanation text to Snwolley TTS API, returns WAV audio |
| `/demo/candles` | GET | Returns historical candle data for replay mode |
| `/demo/replay` | POST | Accepts a date, runs signal engine on that day's data, returns signals |
| `/health` | GET | Health check for deployment |

