## 7. Demo Mode

**Purpose:** Allow judges to see signals immediately without waiting for London open

**How it works:**
- Pre-loaded JSON file contains 30 days of XAUUSD + BTCUSD 15-min historical candles
- Replay engine runs the signal logic on selected day
- User can pick a date from a calendar and see what signals would have fired
- Signals animate onto the screen in real time at 10x speed
- Full signal card, explanation, and voice playback all work in demo mode
- Voice says "Demo signal" at the start so it's clear it's historical

