## 8. UI/UX Design Direction

**Theme:** Dark trading terminal — professional but approachable
**Primary colour:** Deep navy `#0A0F1E`
**Accent:** Electric green `#00FF88` for BUY, Crimson `#FF3B5C` for SELL
**Font:** Inter (clean, modern, readable)
**Card style:** Glassmorphism — subtle blur + border glow
**Mobile first:** All screens designed for 375px width first, scales up to desktop

**Key design decisions:**
- Signal direction (BUY/SELL) is the biggest element on screen — can't miss it
- Dollar amounts are always shown alongside price levels — beginners think in dollars
- Every piece of jargon has a tap-to-explain tooltip
- Loading states are friendly: "PipSense is watching the London session for you..."

